net.nemerosa.ontrack.extension.svn.model

Interface BuildSvnRevisionLink<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of configuration data
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IndexableBuildSvnRevisionLink<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTagBasedSvnRevisionLink, RevisionPatternSvnRevisionLink, RevisionSvnRevisionLink, TagNamePatternSvnRevisionLink, TagNameSvnRevisionLink

    public interface BuildSvnRevisionLink<T>
    Defines the way to link builds to Svn revision, in order to manage the change logs, the Svn searches and synchronisations.
